# AU Micro-SaaS Portfolio — Cursor Pro Models Only (No GPT)
# A$20/mo Cursor Pro | 50-55 bets | cheap workhorse + high-end architect

## Constraint: Cursor Pro models only — NO GPT models
All development AI runs through the Cursor IDE model picker.
**Do not use GPT models** (GPT-5.6 Sol, Luna, Terra, GPT-5.x) — they burn tokens fast.
Use Claude + Gemini + Grok + DeepSeek only. Stay within A$20/mo pool.

## Cursor Pro Model Inventory (No GPT)

### Workhorse — cheap (60-70% of volume, execution)
| Model | Cost | Use for |
|-------|------|---------|
| Haiku 4.5 | $0.80/$4 per M | Cmd+K edits, implementation, refactors |
| Gemini 3.5 Flash | $0.30/$2.50 per M | Boilerplate, config, trivial edits |
| Grok 4.5 | cheap | General workhorse, fast completions |
| DeepSeek V3/R1 | cheap | Specialised code |
| Opus 4.5/4.6/4.7 | FREE in Cursor | Free escalation for schema |

### Architect — high-end (planning + decisions, 5-15 calls/MVP)
| Model | Cost | Use for |
