| Opus 4.8 | $5/$25 per M | Standard architect, schema, fork decisions |
| Fable 5 | $10/$50 per M | Hardest architect, compliance, security audits |
| Sonnet 5 | $2-$3/$10-$15 per M | UI design, agents, complex logic, ISC verify |
